cast.overview: On the brink of turning 30, a promising theater composer navigates love, friendship and the pressure to create something great before time runs out.
cast.title: tick, tick... BOOM!

details.biography: Kate Rockwell (born Katherine Rockwell Wilfong; August 4, 1984)[1] is an American actress, dancer, and singer. She is known for her work on Broadway and for originating the roles of Skylar in Bring It On: The Musical in 2011 and of Karen Smith in the 2018 musical, Mean Girls, for the latter of which she received Drama Desk Award and Helen Hayes Award nominations.
details.name: Kate Rockwell
